sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant B as Browser
    participant A as poc1-app
    participant GH as GitHub OAuth

    B->>A: GET /login
    A->>A: state = random16 (cookie)
    A-->>B: 302 github.com/authorize?state=...

    B->>GH: login + consent
    GH-->>B: 302 /callback?code&state

    B->>A: GET /callback (+ state cookie)
    A->>A: verify state == cookie
    A->>GH: POST /access_token (code + client_secret)
    GH-->>A: access_token
    A->>GH: GET /user
    GH-->>A: {login, name}
    A->>A: jwt.sign(payload, JWT_SECRET, 1h)
    A-->>B: 302 /?token=JWT
    Note over B: JWT in localStorage

    B->>A: GET /me  Authorization: Bearer JWT
    A->>A: jwt.verify(JWT_SECRET)
    A-->>B: {user, name}
